section.heading: New Bethany Baptist Church; Lots 31, 32, and 806, Square 339; and Lots 23, 71, 72, 811, and 812, Square 367.

annotations.annotation: Applicability of D.C. Law 21-145: § 4 of D.C. Law 21-145 provided that the change made to this section by § 2 of D.C. Law 21-145 is subject to the inclusion of the law’s fiscal effect in an approved budget and financial plan. Therefore that amendment has not been given effect.
